comments.body:
I assumed there's no need for tests since this got a NACK.

I was going to check it with tests, but if I undersand it correctly, since we're interested only in wallet transactions, checking if result of `GetWalletTx` is non-`nullptr`would be enough? 
```suggestion
                const CWalletTx* iwtx = pwallet->GetWalletTx(prevout.hash);
                if (!iwtx) continue;
                const CTxOut& txout = iwtx->tx->vout[prevout.n];
```
Or am I missing something again?

